  "title": "Unique Citrusy Malaysian Peppers Curry",
  "description": "A citrusy and cozy Malaysian dish featuring peppers in a glassy-jelly curry, perfect for a cold evening. This gluten-free-friendly recipe is a twist on traditional Malaysian curries.",
